description: The BMO High Yield US Corporate Bond Index ETF has been designed to replicate, to the extent possible, the performance of the Bloomberg U.S. High Yield Very Liquid Index net of expenses. In addition, as ZJK may hold other underlying ETFs, the management fees charged are reduced by the management fees paid on the underlying ETFs, thereby not duplicating the management fees.
name: BMO High Yield US Corporate Bond Index ETF
